          </TabNav>

          <TabNav
            id="tabs-with-card-item-2"
            dataTab="#tabs-with-card-2"
            aria="tabs-with-card-2"
            heading="Technical Publications"
            content="As industry leaders with over three decades of experience, we specialize in high-quality educational publications in Engineering, Pharmacy, and Computer Science. Our portfolio includes over 1000 textbook titles tailored for major Indian universities. With offices in Mumbai, Bangalore, Chennai, and Nasik, our extensive distribution network ensures nationwide coverage. We've also launched an online store to provide a seamless shopping experience, aiming to become India’s premier online destination for educational materials."
