              src={technical_logo}
              alt="Technical Logo"
              class="mt-2 h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 fill-neutral-700 hs-tab-active:fill-[#fa5a15] dark:fill-neutral-300 dark:hs-tab-active:fill-[#3b71fb] md:h-7 md:w-7" />
          </TabNav>

          <TabNav
            id="tabs-with-card-item-3"
            dataTab="#tabs-with-card-3"
            aria="tabs-with-card-3"
            heading="Champ Endurance"
            content="Champ Endurance is a leading fitness community in India that promotes a variety of physical activities like running, swimming, cycling, and sports across the country. They focus on selecting scenic locations for their events to enhance the experience for participants and add value for sponsors. With a vision to build a social-fitness network, they emphasize grassroots events and aim to integrate physical activities into daily life for charitable causes. The team, led by Managing Director Ravindra Wani and CEO Sanjana Lall, organizes major gender-inclusive competitions such as the Apla Pune Marathon & Cyclothon, maintaining strict safety standards. Their philosophy, #GoForMore, encourages participants to continually surpass their achievements.">
